-- 0049_backfill_post_anonymous.sql — restore the historical Discuz
-- pre_forum_post.anonymous=1 set onto the new posts.anonymous column.
--
-- Migration 0047 added the column with DEFAULT 0; without this backfill,
-- every list/forum/search/recommended surface still leaks the original
-- author of every historical anonymous post on any DB that runs the
-- migration chain (prod was hand-fixed, but a fresh test/dev DB applying
-- 0047 then 0048 would land with anonymous=0 across the board, then 0048's
-- own backfill would not flag any thread either).
--
-- Source: 8,474 pids extracted from the 2026-05-20 Discuz dump.
-- Idempotent: setting anonymous=1 on an already-anonymous row is a no-op,
-- and any pid not present in this D1 (pre-migration filtered/corrupt rows)
-- is silently skipped by `WHERE id IN (...)`.

